1. *Suđenje* je počelo u ponedeljak. (The trial began on Monday.)
2. Ne postoji *suđenje* bez optužnice. (There is no trial without an indictment.)
3. On je izražavao svoju želju da se nastavi *suđenje*. (He expressed his desire to continue the trial.)
4. Sudija je odložio *suđenje*. (The judge postponed the trial.)
5. On čeka *suđenje*. (He is awaiting trial.)
6. On je prisustvovao *suđenju*. (He attended the trial.)
7. Oni se spremaju za *suđenje*. (They are preparing for the trial.)